'''Wampa Clan''' was an [[Jedi Initiate/Legends|initiate]] training clan of the [[New Jedi Order]] that was usually made up of children who were fifteen years old. This clan was named after the [[Wampa/Legends|Wampa]], a vicious creature that was native to [[Hoth/Legends|Hoth]]. In [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]], the members of Wampa Clan were taken hostage during the [[Battle of Ossus (Second Galactic Civil War)|occupation of the Jedi Academy]]. They were later rescued and taken to the [[Jedi Outpost]] on [[Endor/Legends|Endor]].

